---

<!-- Education Section (Why) -->
<section id="why" class="py-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-white/[0.01]">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl reveal">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight">Kenapa Bisnis Anda Butuh Lebih dari Sekadar <span class="text-[#6366f1]">Media Sosial?</span></h2>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Di era digital, media sosial adalah <span class="text-white font-bold italic">Brosur</span>, tapi Website adalah <span class="text-[#6366f1] font-bold italic">Kantor Resmi</span>. Pelanggan saat ini semakin kritis; mereka akan mencari "Alamat Digital" Anda di Google sebelum memutuskan untuk bertransaksi.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="glass-card p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 hover:border-[#6366f1]/50 transition-all group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#6366f1]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#6366f1] mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Meningkatkan Kredibilitas</h4>
                <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Bisnis dengan website resmi terlihat 10x lebih terpercaya dibanding hanya lewat DM media sosial.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 hover:border-[#a855f7]/50 transition-all group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#a855f7]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#a855f7] mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Mudah Ditemukan</h4>
                <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Muncul di pencarian Google saat calon pelanggan membutuhkan jasa atau produk Anda di lokasi sekitar.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 hover:border-[#ec4899]/50 transition-all group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#ec4899]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#ec4899] mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Kepemilikan Penuh</h4>
                <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">Anda memegang kendali penuh atas wajah bisnis Anda, tanpa takut algoritma media sosial berubah mendadak.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
